## Reproduce figures and tables

From the package root:

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate  # Windows: .venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

python scripts/generate_all_figures.py
python scripts/compute_scalar_qnm_first_order_wkb.py
```

The WKB scalar-QNM results are a first diagnostic only. They should be replaced or checked against higher-order WKB, shooting, continued fractions, or time-domain evolution before being used as robust QNM predictions.

