## Additional validation scripts in v0.3.4

This release adds lightweight symbolic validation scripts:

```bash
python scripts/verify_curvature_invariants.py
python scripts/derive_isco_polynomial.py
python scripts/derive_energy_conditions.py
```

These scripts print `PASS` where an algebraic check is successful. They are not substitutes for external review, but they improve reproducibility of the analytic derivations.
